race.comment: LOLLY MONELLI (7) is racing well without winning, recording nine minors on end, the latest when collided in the run and finishing second in a Maiden at this track (22.87). Rates a top chance. SMILE TIME (3) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant fourth (23.21) in a Maiden over 400m at this track. Rates a leading chance on best. KOMBI ACKEE (1) is overdue for a maiden success having placed at three of nine starts, the latest missing the frame when seventh at this track. Better than last start and can bounce back. KRATOS MISSILE (5) warrants respect following a recent placing.
